body_html: After brief investigation of generated caffe2_pybind11_state.vcxproj for both BUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON and OFF configurations, I see onnx libs are not being linked, when building with BUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON. Why is that? Should I build it on my own and provide it to the linker?
